OL,3,CPay parity for NI healthcare workers
OL,4,Cto be delivered
OL,6,FHealthcare workers in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fare to receive a pay uplift that will
OL,8,Frestore parity with the rest of the
OL,9,FUK, Health Minister Mike Nesbitt has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe announcement delivers uplifts as
OL,13,Frecommended by pay review bodies in
OL,14,FApril.
OL,16,FNurses in the region had warned of
OL,17,Fimminent strike action if a 3.6%
OL,18,Fincrease recommended by the
OL,19,Findependent Pay Review Body was not
OL,20,Fmet.
