OL,6,FHe said: "It is hugely disappointing
OL,7,Fthat it has taken so long to resolve
OL,8,Fthis and we sincerely hope lessons
OL,9,Fhave indeed been learnt and pay will
OL,10,Fbe prioritised in next year's
OL,11,Fbudgeting process.
OL,13,F"The goodwill of doctors has been
OL,14,Fstretched to breaking point."
OL,16,FRepresentatives of the Royal College
OL,17,Fof Nursing (RCN) met Mr Nesbitt on
OL,18,FThursday.
