OL,6,FRita Devlin, executive director of the
OL,7,FRCN in Northern Ireland said: "This
OL,8,Fhas been a long and protracted process
OL,9,Fto get to this stage, and we welcome
OL,10,Fthe confirmation that pay parity will
OL,11,Fbe reinstated for hard working health
OL,12,Fcare staff.
OL,14,F"The Royal College of Nursing has
OL,15,Fconsistently maintained that the loss
OL,16,Fof pay parity with colleagues across
OL,17,Fthe UK was wholly unacceptable.
