OL,6,F"Our members have expressed deep
OL,7,Ffrustration over this issue, and we
OL,8,Fwelcome the minister's commitment to
OL,9,Fensuring the late payment of pay
OL,10,Fawards will never happen again.
OL,12,F"We will now examine the proposal in
OL,13,Ffurther detail and take it to the RCN
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland Board for discussion."
