OL,6,FMr Nesbitt announced in May that he
OL,7,Fhad signed off the pay award in line
OL,8,Fwith the Pay Review Body (PRB)
OL,9,Frecommendation of a 3.6% pay rise for
OL,10,Fhealth workers in Northern Ireland,
OL,11,Fbut said the money would have to be
OL,12,Ffound by the powersharing Executive
OL,13,Fbecause he is facing a funding
OL,14,Fshortfall in his department.
OL,16,FLast month, he said only half of the
OL,17,Fmoney needed to resolve the pay award
OL,18,Fhad been found and negotiations were
OL,19,Fcontinuing.
